        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶是二物有對。",
        "translation": "It's still like saying the two things are opposites.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c04_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖復合而為一。",
        "translation": "Even though they are again combined into one, they still remain one.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c05_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶存一也。",
        "translation": "They still remain one.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c05_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其實我所說色。",
        "translation": "In fact, what I've said about form ...",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c05_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即是說空。",
        "translation": "That's what I mean by emptiness.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c05_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "色之外無空矣。",
        "translation": "There's no emptiness outside of form.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c06_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我所說空。",
        "translation": "What I've described as emptiness is the same as describing form.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c06_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即是說色。",
        "translation": "That is, I'm talking about form.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c06_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "空之外無色矣。",
        "translation": "There's no form outside of emptiness.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c06_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非但無色。",
        "translation": "It's not just that there's no form.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c07_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而亦無空。",
        "translation": "There's also no emptiness.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c07_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此真空也。",
        "translation": "This is also emptiness.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c07_23",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故又呼而告之曰。",
        "translation": "Therefore, he also called out to them and told them.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c07_24",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子。",
        "translation": "\"Śāriputra!",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c08_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是諸法空相。",
        "translation": "\"These things are empty in their characteristics.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c08_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無空可名。",
        "translation": "There's no emptiness to be called.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c08_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何況更有生滅垢淨增減名相。",
