        "translation": "The six sense-fields are empty.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c12_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無色聲香味觸法也。",
        "translation": "There's no form, sound, smells, tastes, and tactile objects.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c12_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十八界皆空。",
        "translation": "The eighteen elements are empty.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0830c12_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無眼界乃至無意識界也。",
        "translation": "There's no element of vision ... and no element of consciousness.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a01_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以至生老病死。",
        "translation": "It goes on to birth, aging, illness, and death.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a01_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "明與無明。",
        "translation": "insight and ignorance.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a01_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四諦智證等皆無所得。",
        "translation": "knowledge of the four truths and so forth are unobtainable.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a02_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此自在菩薩智慧觀照到無所得之彼岸也如此。",
        "translation": "This is how the Freely Awakened Bodhisattva's wisdom and insight reach the other shore of attaining nothing.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a02_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所得既無。",
        "translation": "Once what's attained is nonexistent, then there's naturally no obstruction, fear, or mistakenness on the part of others.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a03_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自然無罣礙恐怖與夫顛倒夢想矣。",
        "translation": "naturally, there are no obstructions, fears, or mistaken dreams of men.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a03_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "現視生死。",
        "translation": "He'll now see birth and death.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a04_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而究竟涅槃矣。",
        "translation": "He'll now attain final nirvāṇa.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a04_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "豈惟菩薩。",
        "translation": "Isn't it just the bodhisattvas?",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a04_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖過去現在未來三世諸佛。",
        "translation": "It's the wisdom of the buddhas of the three past, present, and future generations.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a05_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦以此智慧。",
        "translation": "By this wisdom, they'll also attain the other shore.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a05_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
