        "translation": "They'll reach the other shore together.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a05_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "共成無上正等正覺焉耳。",
        "translation": "They'll all become unsurpassed, perfectly enlightened, and completely enlightened.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a06_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "則信乎盡大地眾生。",
        "translation": "Then, it's believed that as many sentient beings as possible on earth.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a06_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有不是佛者。",
        "translation": "There's no one who isn't a buddha.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a07_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃知此真空妙智。",
        "translation": "Then they'll know that this marvelous wisdom of the vacuum.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a07_1",
