        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a08_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能出離生死苦海。",
        "translation": "It's a spell that can escape the ocean of suffering through birth and death.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a08_6",
