    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩豈異人哉。",
        "translation": "Isn't the bodhisattva different from other people?",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a14_26",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但能一觀照之焉耳。",
        "translation": "They can simply observe and illuminate it once.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a14_27",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "人人皆菩薩。",
        "translation": "Everyone is a bodhisattva.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a15_28",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而不自見也。",
        "translation": "They don't see it for themselves.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a15_29",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故言菩薩。",
        "translation": "That's why they say bodhisattva.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a15_30",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "則人人一矣。",
        "translation": "\"Everyone is one.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a15_31",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無聖愚也。",
        "translation": "There are no noble or foolish ones.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a16_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "言三世諸佛。",
        "translation": "They say the buddhas of the three times are one.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a16_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "則古今一矣。",
        "translation": "Then, the past and present are one.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a16_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無先後也。",
        "translation": "There's no prior or subsequent one.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a16_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "奈之何可使由而不可使知者眾也。",
        "translation": "How could it be that there are so many things that can be made to come from and so many things that can't be made known?",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a16_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "可使知。",
        "translation": "They can be made to know.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a17_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "則為菩薩。",
        "translation": "They're bodhisattvas.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a17_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不可使知。",
        "translation": "When they can't be made to know, they're a bodhisattva.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a17_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "則為凡民。",
        "translation": "They'll be ordinary people.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a18_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為禽獸。",
        "translation": "They'll be animals ...",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a18_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為木石。",
        "translation": "They're made of wood and stone.",
        "source": "X26n0543_001:0831a18_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "卒歸於泯泯爾矣。",
        "translation": "In the end, they all return to extinction.",
